<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>Project-Tesco Redundancy Calculator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/AddColleague.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="colleague-main">
        <h1>Add Colleague</h1>
        <hr />

        <div class="note-container">
            <div class="logo1">
                <img src=@alert alt="Menu" >
                <span>Note</span>

            </div>
            <div class="note">
                <span>
                    This page can be used to add colleagues to your project.<br />
                    if the colleague details are held in the database, the colleague data will prepopulate, if they are not in the database
                    you will be required to enter the data
